obj_root_law_translations_hi_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE MAHATMA GANDHI ANTARRASHTRIYA HINDI VISHWAVIDYALAYA`
  line `ACT, 1996`
  line __________________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line __________________
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `3. Establishment of the University.`
  line `4. Objects of the University.`
  line `5. Powers of the University.`
  line `6. Jurisdiction.`
  line `7. University open to all classes, castes and creeds.`
  line `8. Residence of students.`
  line `9. The Visitor.`
  line `10. Officers of the University.`
  line `11. The Chancellor.`
  line `12. The Vice-Chancellor.`
  line `13. The Pro-Vice-Chancellor.`
  line `14. The Deans of Schools.`
  line `15. The Registrar.`
  line `16. The Finance Officer.`
  line `17. The Librarian.`
  line `18. Other Officers.`
  line `19. Authorities of the University.`
  line `20. The Court.`
  line `21. The Executive Council.`
  line `22. The Academic Council.`
  line `23. The Board of Studies.`
  line `24. The Finance Committee.`
  line `25. Other authorities of the University.`
  line `26. Power to make Statutes.`
  line `27. Statutes how to be made.`
  line `28. Powers to make Ordinances.`
  line `29. Regulations.`
  line `30. Annual report.`
  line `31. Annual accounts.`
  line `32. Conditions of service of employees.`
  line `33. Procedure of appeal and arbitration in disciplinary cases against students.`
  line `34. Right to appeal.`
  line `35. Provident and pension funds.`
  line `36. Disputes as to constitution of University authorities and bodies.`
  line `37. Constitution of Committees.`
  line `38. Filling of casual vacancies.`
  line `39. Proceedings of University authorities or bodies not invalidated by vacancies.`
  line `40. Protection of action taken in good faith.`
  line `41. Mode of proof of University record.`
